description: The Digital Agency Starter Kit is a free solution developed by ByteAnt company in 2023. It is designed specifically for Umbraco 12.0.0 and is a feature-rich, easy-to-use starter kit. ByteAnt's expertise was utilized in crafting this solution, which is tailored to the needs of digital agencies, start-ups, and technology companies.
